<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063658" n="1"/>
  <opener><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2925535"><abbr>Ffurt.</abbr></rs> <date when="1716-09-04">4 <abbr>Sept.</abbr> 1716</date>.</dateline>
    <lb/><salute>Viro Celeberrimo at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Doctissimo 
      <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450" >
      <lb/><abbr>Jac.</abbr> Hermannus</rs>
      <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Paucissima h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cce qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> inter alias negotiorum curas deproperare potui Tibi debeo ut l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>titiam
    <lb/>meam Tibi tester ex gratissimo mihi nuntio quod deni<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <abbr>Excell.</abbr> <rs type="person">Reformatores</rs> <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Patavi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>n<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><orig>TE</orig><reg>Te</reg></choice> ad publice docenda <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> Mathemata asciverint orto, hunc<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> honorem tanto impensius Tibi
    <lb/>gratulor quanto magis hunc eventum prosperum in votis habui at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad eum obtinendum meas etiam curas
    <lb/>posui quod ex eo facile conjectare potes, quod rogatus <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Michelotto</rs> numquid ad pristinam stationem redire
    <lb/>vellem cum aucto us<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad alterum tantum salario? respui oblationem ea potissimum de causa ne hoc pacto Tibi
    <lb/>impedimento essem ut diserte <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Michelotto</rs> significavi, alioqui facillime adduci potuissem ut pristinum locum
    <lb/>repeterem lautioribus quam antea sub conditionibus iis<add>dem scilicet</add> quas <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Amicus</rs> noster co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unis proposuerat, faxit Deus ut
    <lb/>integra valetudine Provinciam hanc novam ea cum laude qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Nomen Tuum nunquam non comitari solet,
    <lb/>exornare queas. Lectiones vero Tuas non nisi circa medium aut finem <date>Novembris</date> auspicari poteris, quia prius s<unclear>ingulos</unclear>
    <lb/><rs type="person">Professores</rs> legentes audire debebis priusquam <rs type="biblio">Orationem Tuam inauguralem</rs> habere possis cui <rs type="person">Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tor</rs> et <rs type="person">Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>su<unclear>lus</unclear></rs>
    <lb/><rs type="place">Civitatis</rs> qui ambo sunt <rs type="person">Patritii Veneti</rs> interesse solent, <rs type="biblio">oratio</rs> ista non ex scripto legi sed memoriter recitari solet. Quod ad
    <lb/>Lectiones attinet duodecim vel 14 prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> reliquis magis elaborari merentur quia hisce maximus Auditorum
    <lb/>confluxus interesse consuevit propter rei novitatem, in reliquis materiam Tuam didactice prout decet pertractare
    <lb/>poteris. Necessitas me satis operosam quidem sed utilem tamen in Lectionib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> viam inire fecit, scilicet singulis scamnis
    <lb/>unum exemplum seu paginam figuras illas continentem quas in discursu explicaturus eram imponi curavi ut eas
    <lb/>cominus Auditores inspicere et contemplari possent, hac ratione et ego exemplum figurar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in manu tenens facile
    <lb/>et sine memori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> onere argument<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> meum explicare potuerim cum coeteri <rs type="person">Professores</rs> memoriter Lectiones recitando
    <lb/>non mediocrem subinde memori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> torturam ut sic barbare loquar, patiun<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>. In delectu materi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Mathematico publica Auto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ritate nihil pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>scribitur, propterea ego primo anno explicui elementa Geometri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, Trigonometriam et Geometriam practicam<supplied>,</supplied>
    <lb/>Secundo Mechanicam, Tertio Hydrostaticam et <rs type="keyword">Hydraulicam</rs>, quarto <rs type="keyword">Opticam Catoptricam</rs> et <rs type="keyword">Dioptricam</rs>, quinto doctrin<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
    <lb/><rs type="keyword">Sph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ricam Gnomonicam</rs> et <rs type="keyword">Astrolabiorum</rs> structuram; sic qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tibi factu magis consulta videbuntur Tute eliges pro
    <lb/>arbitrio Tuo. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c pauca sunt qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> circa lectiones meas notare potui <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728"><choice><orig>patavii</orig><reg>Patavii</reg></choice></rs> habitas. Gratias habeo maximas pro eo quo
    <lb/>mihi polliceris Te <del/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> qualiscun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> fam<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> rationem habiturum quam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzalia</rs> in nupero <rs type="biblio">scripto</rs> vel poti<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> libello famoso
    <lb/>pessundare omnibus viribus sed stultissimis rationib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> conat<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> est, videbis tot et tantis <rs type="biblio">scriptum</rs> ejus scatere paralogismis ut mihi
    <lb/>indecens esse putem cum homine impudentissimo disputationis serram ulterius reciprocare, nonnulla insunt eidem <rs type="biblio">scripto</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>nec Tibi valde placitura sunt, si tempus et spatium permitterent, excerptum e<add>arum</add> huc transcriberem, sed brevi forte Tuismet
    <lb/>oculis quicquid rei est videbis. Problema a Te proposit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Italis</rs> solvere aggressus <choice><orig><g ref="#est">[est]</g></orig><reg>est</reg></choice>, sed ita de illo loquitur ut ejus sens<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice><!-- Weiser -->
    <pb facs="1063660" n="3"/>minime assequut<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> e<choice><orig><g ref="#sse">[sse]</g></orig><reg>sse</reg></choice> videatur, dum distinguit inter distantiam finitam et infinitam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> centro. Quando de hoc problemate sermo recurrit
    <lb/><rs type="person">Checcocius</rs> mihi <rs type="letter">scribit</rs> se solam Solutionis su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Syntheticam demonstrationem dedisse se<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> adeo non videre qui analysin <add>suam</add> a Te non visam
    <lb/>petitionis principii accusare potueris. Ais neminem genuinam <abbr>Probl.</abbr> Tui solutionem daturum nisi generale solverit ex data scala temporum
    <lb/>invenire scalam virium aut vicissim. Si non fallor ego demonstrare possum generaliter loquendo <hi rend="u">problema solvi non posse seu implicare</hi>
    <lb/>et ex eadem hac demonstratione seu fundamento ejus postea deduco solutionem Problematis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <choice><orig>TE</orig><reg>Te</reg></choice> propositi et reperio curvam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation"></pc><lb break="no"/>sitam esse parabolam cubicam; sed si scala temporis esset curva alius generis quam parabolici verbi gratia Hyperbola non inter
    <lb/>asymptotas sed ad axem relata hoc casu nulla potest assignari scala virium.</p>
  <p><lb/>Postrem<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> gratias habeo pro amica doloris testificatione occasione inopinati obitus <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-142566241">Frizii</rs> Affinis mei jucundissimi
    <lb/>faxit Deus ut ad par officii genus per longissimum tempus erga Te non tenear, quin potius Te <add>et</add> <abbr>Ampliss.</abbr> <rs type="person">Parentem</rs> perinde
    <lb/>ac totam honoratissimam familiam omnigena benedictione ubertim cumulet quam diutissime.</p>
  <closer>Vale et me ama.
    <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2925535"><abbr>Ffurti ad Oderam</abbr></rs>
      <lb/><date when="1716-09-04">4 <abbr>Sept.</abbr> 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript>
<p><lb/>Ignosce confus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scriptioni quam
  <lb/>ne quidem relegere mihi integrum est per temporis angustiam.</p>
</postscript>
